    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界观舞台是建立在多样行星构成的宇宙上，不同派系以卡牌与战术对局争夺殖民权与主导地位。世界观随星球而异，胜负取决于你的构筑与决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一颗星球，都是一个截然不同的世界观——<br>中古奇幻、蒸气工业、魔法文明、科技霸权、原始部落……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/900ce0c0b7b3cc61c5339f34644ead29.poster.avif?t=1772456999\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/900ce0c0b7b3cc61c5339f34644ead29.webm?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/900ce0c0b7b3cc61c5339f34644ead29.mp4?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 游戏特色</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >♟ 策略棋盘 × 卡牌对战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是单纯的卡牌对局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场是一个 <strong>8×8 的战略棋盘</strong>，<br>每一次出牌，都是一次位置、时机与资源的抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以召唤单位、建造设施、部署陷阱，<br>逐步构筑属于你的战术前线。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌具备如 <strong>炉石战记</strong>、<strong>魔法风云会</strong> 般清楚、可预期的效果设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋盘布局与站位，承袭战棋游戏的空间思考</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双费用资源系统，带来更深层的组牌与决策空间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前线、防禦、区域攻击、多方向选取等複合战术可自由组合</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一回合，都是策略与预判的正面交锋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🃏 自定义卡组，自行发展战术方向</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以依据卡牌效果、资源配置与棋盘互动方式，<br>自由组合出不同的对战策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏不预设固定流派，也不限制标准解法。<br>每一副卡组，都是玩家在规则框架下的个人选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑的差异，将直接影响你在对局中的节奏、资源运用与战术取捨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b5a26b232dcfa3657d81f30db3c43534.poster.avif?t=1772456999\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b5a26b232dcfa3657d81f30db3c43534.webm?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b5a26b232dcfa3657d81f30db3c43534.mp4?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌工艺系统允许你分解不需要的卡牌，製作游戏中几乎所有卡片；<br>卡包设计同时兼顾新手体验与长期公平性：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡册未满 30 张前，抽取卡牌<strong>不会重複</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传奇卡牌具备保底机制，<strong>最多 41 抽必定获得</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b3b960ce79c9652725a16b437e3c677f.poster.avif?t=1772456999\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b3b960ce79c9652725a16b437e3c677f.webm?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294170/extras/b3b960ce79c9652725a16b437e3c677f.mp4?t=1772456999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌐 即时连线对战 / 排位挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与来自世界各地的探险者进行即时对战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要精准配置棋盘、预判对手行动、有效管理资源，<br>才能在每一场交锋中取得优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来将陆续加入：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >季节制排位系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专精战术路线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阵营特化与环境加成玩法</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战局会变，但策略深度只会持续堆叠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 为策略玩家而生的作品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你热爱：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>炉石战记</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔法风云会</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战棋类游戏（如 <strong>Fire Emblem</strong>、<strong>Into the Breach</strong>）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度组牌、资源管理与长线策略思考</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那麽这款融合 <strong>卡牌 × 棋盘 × 星际探险</strong> 的策略游戏，<br>将为你带来不同于既有作品的全新体验。</p>",
